 2000-04732000-03-300,  ,  TB,  AGRI-FOOD,  ,  ,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisAuthority for the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into ADJUSTMENT PROGRAM AGREEMENTS with Saskatchewan and Manitoba to provide for payment to grain, oilseed and specialty crop producers to allow them to complete the adjustment to increased transportation costs during a period of low commodity prices.
